  <p>Welcome to Project Sites, operated by Megabyte LLC ("we," "us," or "our"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website at <a href="https://sites.megabyte.space">sites.megabyte.space</a> and use our services.</p>

